orizontal exit</xref>; and</li><li id="_ca5aa335-e34a-4baa-8c49-32feb35e404c">door serving as, or forming part of, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_afdaea08-80ca-4098-ac64-e30179dd52ea" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_0702fa67-33d2-447c-a3f8-8af9b7f55981" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_a175aacb-1c87-43e8-a797-2b97b3ffb803" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_7919dabd-58f3-49b3-91fa-36a8af2bfb97" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be provided with emergency lighting in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2827_2.2.0.xml#_8d4e5213-2e19-4a0c-b55a-e8afe0bcfa17" id="_e8a24cb7-1441-4166-9be4-fc79c01d8b27" scope="local" type="clause">E4D2</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>